                              Regional Overview
     __________________________________________________________________

                            [USEMAP:Arleneh.jpg]
            FAA Eastern Regional Administrator Arlene B. Feldman

                                 Manny Weiss
                   Regional Executive Manager Manny Weiss

   Welcome to the Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) Eastern Region
   Information Site. The purpose of this site is to provide you with as
   much information as possible about the Eastern Region and the FAA
   overall.

   The Regional Administrator is responsible for maintaining oversight and
   for appraising overall mission accomplishment within the region. The
   Regional Administrator provides executive direction for local
   multi-program issues including operational emergency activities.
   Additional responsibilities include interfacing with industry, the
   public, and various Congressional offices and other government bodies
   at the regional level. The Regional Executive Manager serves as Acting
   Regional Administrator in the absence of the Regional Administrator.

   Feel free to browse the pages of our site to find out any information
   that you need.

   The content of these pages is unofficial and not authority for action.
   Views, opinions and data expressed or represented, do not necessarily
   reflect those of the U.S. Department of Transportation of the Federal
   Aviation Administration.
